flowchart TD
    A[Customer starts order session] --> B[Select menu items]
    B --> C[Create order via OrderService]
    C --> D{Payment confirmed by Hubtel callback?}

    D -->|Yes| E[Mark order as Paid via OrderService]
    D -->|No callback after 5 min| F[Run transaction status check]
    F --> G{Status is Paid?}
    G -->|Yes| E
    G -->|No| H[Keep order Unpaid/Failed and notify customer if needed]

    E --> I{Delivery or Pickup?}
    I -->|Pickup| J[Prepare and complete pickup order]
    I -->|Delivery| K[Generate random 6-digit delivery code]
    K --> L[Hash and store code]
    L --> M[Attempt delivery verification]
    M --> N{Code valid?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Complete delivery]
    N -->|No| P[Increment attempt counter]
    P --> Q{Attempts >= 3?}
    Q -->|No| M
    Q -->|Yes| R[Block completion and escalate]

O --> S["Issue loyalty points: floor(order_total / 35) * 5"]
    J --> S
    S --> T[Send completion SMS]

    U{Order returned/refunded?} -->|Yes| V[Do NOT award loyalty]
    U -->|Yes| W[Send returned-order SMS + log rider_id]
